

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-1"></div>
  <div class="col-md-6"><br>
    <p>There are <%= @stations.count %> stations total</p>
    <p>The average bikes available per station is <%= @stations.average_bikes %></p>
    <p>The most bikes at a station is <%= @stations.most_bikes %> bikes</p>
    <p>The station(s) where the most bikes are available is/are <%= @stations.station_with_most_bikes %></p>
    <p>The fewest bikes at a station is <%= @stations.fewest_bikes %> bikes</p>
    <p>The station(s) where the least bikes are available is/are <%= @stations.station_with_fewest_bikes %></p>
    <p>The most recently installed station is <%= @stations.most_recent_station %></p>
    <p>The oldest station is <%= @stations.oldest_station %></p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary active btn-sm formbtn" href="/stations/new">Create a Station</a><br><br>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <p><%= pie_chart Station.group(:city).count %></p>
  </div>

</div>
